zm_Lila_Panic_Unlimited_72_v2_LDR - this is zm_lila_panic in a new version, added a lot of new nooks, on the map added normal lighting, now the map is more pleasant to play on, but there are places where textures are missing (pink textures), so don't get scared, the problem is not you!
